oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.socialnetwork.model.pojo
Class SocialNetworkTreeDataCollector

java.lang.Object
  oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.socialnetwork.model.pojo.SocialNetworkTreeDataCollector

public class SocialNetworkTreeDataCollector
extends java.lang.Object

Temporary object used during tree creation to consolidate the additional pieces of information that are needed whilst the tree is being created. Most of the data contained directly within will be expected to be released after the tree creation has finished however it does contain a proxy to an internal reference to a SocialNetworkStructureStorage that is intended to survive after the tree creation process.
